  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level, your soul becomes potent enough to maintain itself while seperated from you. When you would use your <em><strong>Soul Manifestation</strong></em> feature, you may spend an additional <strong>Martial Die</strong>. When you do this, your soul manifests itself in it's full form. During this, you gain the following benefits in addition to your Soul Manifestation features;</p><ul><li>Your Unarmed Attacks now have the reach 2 property and all Taijutsu you cast have their range increased by 10 feet.</li><li>When a creature hits you with an attack roll, you reduce the damage taken by the result of 1 <strong>Martial Die</strong>. This does not spend the die.</li><li>You cannot suffer a penalty to attack bonus or saving throws from mental conditions.</li><li>When a taijutsu you cast would inflict a condition, you may instead inflict an equivalent amount of ranks of fear or charmed until the end of your next turn.</li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
    },
